<em>Medeski</em>:  For me, the most important thing is the music effects people in a way that gives them something - whatever it is - that takes them somewhere or makes them think.  Music gives you so many different things.  It can make you think.  It can make you feel so many different things.  And I think that's the most important thing.

And I think that with this band, it is that - it is uplifting.  The music is uplifting.

